<p style=3D"font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.6; margin:=
 0; margin-bottom: 10px;"><i>By Kyle Drennen</i></p>
<p style=3D"font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.6; margin:=
 0; margin-bottom: 10px;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.6; margin:=
 0; margin-bottom: 10px;">During an interview with Senator Marco Rubio on T=
uesday, PBS host Charlie Rose urged the Florida Republican to say something=
 positive about ObamaCare: <b>"What's the best thing you can say about the =
Affordable Care Act?" </b>Rubio replied: "That it's forced us to have a deb=
ate about health insurance in America." Rose fretted: "That's it?"</p>
<p style=3D"font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.6; margin:=
 0; margin-bottom: 10px;">Rose tried to push supportive spin on the unpopul=
ar policy: "In terms of accessibility, in terms of &ndash; it has not been =
as &ndash; I mean, the projected costs have not been as bad as they assumed=
." Rubio countered: "They've not been as good as they proclaimed either."</=
p>
<p style=3D"font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.6; margin:=
 0; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center;"><br><a style=3D"color: #2b63c=
b; text-decoration: none;" href=3D"http://email.mrc.org/c/13zSiSWHUZPtMYxC5=
tR6eV1"><img style=3D"max-width: 100=3D"http://msgfocus.com/files/amf_paramount/workspace_7/icon_play_25x25.png=
" alt=3D""><span style=3D"font-size: 24px;">View video on MRCTV</span></a><=
/p>
<p style=3D"font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.6; margin:=
 0; margin-bottom: 10px;">Rose pressed: "Yeah, but have been less than was =
assumed." Rubio explained:</p>
<p style=3D"font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.6; margin:=
 0; margin-bottom: 10px;">But the costs really are bearing out on the consu=
mer side as well. Because for example, people thought, "Okay, now I'm going=
 to have this free health insurance, and by the way, I'm going to get a sub=
sidy for it." And then they realized that before they can even begin to use=
 that insurance, they've got to come with $4,000 as part of their ctibl=
e. So they're really not insured.</p>
<p style=3D"font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.6; margin:=
 0; margin-bottom: 10px;">Rose and Rubio also had a <a style=3D"color: #2b6=
3cb; text-decoration: none;" href=3D"http://email.mrc.org/c/13zSupi10k4kZ4H=
obBkctQY" target=3D"_blank">contentious exchange</a> on Monday's <i>CBS Thi=
s Morning</i>, when Rose tried to argue that President Obama reopening dipl=
omatic relations with Cuba would bring about political reform in the totali=
tarian regime.</p>
<p style=3D"font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.6; margin:=
 0; margin-bottom: 10px;">Here is a transcript of the exchange on the Janua=
ry 14 edition of Rose's PBS program:</p>
<blockquote>
